OL,3,CDemolition set to start on Clifton
OL,4,CBridge as M6 remains shut in both
OL,5,Cdirections
OL,7,FAs motorists and rail users experience
OL,8,Fmajor disruption, people are warned
OL,9,Fthey could be fined if they don't
OL,10,Fstick to diversion routes.
OL,12,FThe Clifton Bridge carries the West
OL,13,FCoast Mainline over the motorway
OL,14,Fbetween junction 39 at Shap and
OL,15,Fjunction 40 at Penrith.
OL,17,FPreparatory work to demolish the 60
OL,18,Fyear old structure began this morning
OL,19,F(Saturday) and will continue across
OL,20,Fthis weekend, and next weekend.
