OL,3,CDemolition set to start on Clifton
OL,4,CBridge as M6 remains shut in both
OL,5,Cdirections
OL,7,FIts set to be replaced by a new 130m
OL,8,Flong bridge which just needs to be
OL,9,Fmoved into place from a nearby holding
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FThe work will partially close the M6
OL,13,Fon two weekends, while train
OL,14,Ftravellers will have to endure an hour-
OL,15,Flong diversion if travelling between
OL,16,FCarlisle and Preston.
OL,18,FPeople are being urged to check before
OL,19,Fthey travel and adhere to the
OL,20,Fdiversions which are put in place or
OL,21,Frisk a fine.
