OL,7,FNational Highways say there will be a
OL,8,Fpermit system where only those with
OL,9,Fpermits will be able to access local
OL,10,Froads.
OL,12,F"If you're being diverted, stay on the
OL,13,Fdiversion routes, if you're local, you
OL,14,Fcan use the local local roads,"
OL,15,Fexplains Steve Mason from National
OL,16,FHighways,
