OL,3,CDemolition set to start on Clifton
OL,4,CBridge as M6 remains shut in both
OL,5,Cdirections
OL,7,F"As you can imagine lots of the local
OL,8,Froads will not be treated in winter,
OL,9,Fthey're very small, narrow back roads,
OL,10,Fwith weak bridges etcetera and we want
OL,11,Fto protect those from the onslaught of
OL,12,Fthe of the diverted traffic.
OL,14,F"We have police units available, so 3
OL,15,Funits who will patrol the area and if
OL,16,Fwe find some routes are being abused
OL,17,Fwith multiple vehicles using that
OL,18,Froute we will ask the police to go and
OL,19,Fstop those motorists and ask them to
OL,20,Fdeal with those who shouldn't really
OL,21,Fbe there."
